"The investigation continues, for the moment no definite hypotheses have been made public," Peskov said, questioned why Putin's official statements were not mentioned in the Islamic State. "We spoke only of preliminary data, there is no hypothesis yet," he explained and insisted: "We have to wait for information from security forces."
